升高血糖的风险，原理是它会破坏我们的肠道菌群；但是并不能因此说‘人工甜味剂有毒’，不同人群，影响存在差异；就算是糖尿病人，血糖的上升和食用人工甜味剂的关系也不是必然，还要考虑病情和食用量。此外，甜味剂对现代食品工业本身还是做出了很大的贡献。」王思露表示。（时代周报）"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-8350ba2b233df311ee73ccc518be25c6_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "76 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/454816440"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I8/zxku2B/fgTEAMaCDYzMzUwMTY5INvV4IMGMAA4LEAVcgk0NTQ4MTY0NDB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1618533159.9133632", "card_id": "Q_61341208", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 91}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "减肥对一个人的外貌改变有多大？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-cb69570efe3dfa6492c47e95f00f3cda_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "75 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/61341208"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I8/zxku2B/fgTEAMaCDE2NzYwNzk4IMjZpMoFMAA43QJAFnIINjEzNDEyMDh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "23_1618533159.9136662", "card_id": "Q_454443862", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 124}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "后疫情时代，汽车如何保障我们的健康出行？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "汽车早已不是单纯的出行工具，当出行健康越来越受到消费者的重视，如何利用科技保障健康出行？汽车能否成为健康防护与检测的载体？ 了解更多：科技颠覆想象"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-8cce032dfbff6211b7cf408b6f234421_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "71 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/454443862"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I8/zxku2B/fgTEAMaCDYzMjY3MTQ4IM7a1YMGMAA4mAFAF3IJNDU0NDQzODYyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "24_1618533159.914033", "card_id": "Q_279205349", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 3